Lyrics
======

Description
-----------

Fetches current song from MPD (simple modification to fit other players),
downloads lyrics from lyrics.wikia.com and outputs to stdout (using less if
output is longer than console)

Usage
-----

% lyrics


Note on other players
---------------------

In order to work with other players, delete line 25 and assign variable current
data from your player in format: "artist:title" (may contain spaces)


